Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.59,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.75,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.50,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.31,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.45,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:22.80,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:27.53,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:34.47,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it out loud, you love Takehiko Henmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:02:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you admitted this girl, Misonoo Nanako, into the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted her to worship you so much that she would leave Henmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Misonoo Nanako, first year, section B...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...for certain personal reasons, hereby resign from the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,26. The Promise in the Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not speaking to me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I said "good morning" and you just mumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night at the Sorority house!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened with Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...about what happened with Miya-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...or with Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or that I have written a letter of resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to speak to Miya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a cold. She's resting at her summer place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...her summer place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That summer place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Rei, today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for her since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an exhibition game tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd asked her to lend a hand, but I guess she won't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you remind her if you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her it's at the auditorium at 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right my Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The one suffering the most from all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...might actually be Saint-Juste-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She, who has eyes only for Miya-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...now knows that Miya-sama is in love with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother had just died,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...and your family was about to adopt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Around that time, you took a trip to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me that you had a sudden desire to see the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I knew perfectly well the real reason for the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Those fiercely proud eyes of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...they told me the real story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, when I was a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...I collected glass miniatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Glass has such purity, such clarity...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicate and glowing... I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day one of the maids was cleaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...and carelessly broke one of the pieces I had on the shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I immediately smashed all the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,With my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I had to. Otherwise, someone might have broken another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can break or defile the things I cherish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't. I'll never allow it! It would be unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But for us, it's still not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not too late to seal our beautiful time forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will ever desecrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you would...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be joining you. Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're there, aren't you, Saint-Juste-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:08:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? I'm coming right over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of soup do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegetable? Chicken? My Chinese soup is good, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my Brother... I thought I'd cook something for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only thing I can do for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If she falls asleep, or won't talk, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she won't so much as smile... it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it you are seeing Rei today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I... thought she'd like some soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not necessary. She doesn't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't need anything. Go on back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go home! I won't go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I... here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm crushed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts that you misunderstood me so!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only exchanging letters with my Brother! That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look in on that girl myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on now. Back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how cold her room is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How she's always alone, and never eats...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I said I'd be with her, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! You never do anything for Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose your words with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am her sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would join me. I waited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed that you would join me soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was there waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The cold of the snow was so comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As I was losing consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...I felt that you were there watching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The snow's coldness was soon replaced with warmth, softness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I drifted into a flowering springtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I knew my body temperature was falling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...my consciousness began to fade,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I remember nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When I woke up, I was in a hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And there you were... you were at my bedside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You tilted your head and looked at me intently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other side of the window, it was still snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still remember the sound of the falling snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Koto koto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Koto koto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Koton koton...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Koto koto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Koto koto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Koton...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen here, fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an import. So, how about 25,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'll give you a discount even.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lets see your wallet... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Some time passed, and you came to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It turned out I wasn't to be living with the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, I'd be alone in an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So you paid me a visit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:15:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'd like to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't live with you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...but take this doll in my place, to remind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I will honor my promise, and try again with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this bracelet as a token of my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, will you wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad, isn't it, how you and I ended up being such wonderful sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's so sad that we have different mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The more we come to like each others, the more it disturbs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So before sadness overtakes us... before it's too late for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you who first said it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's just end it all."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But then... after all that... you didn't join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help me, someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help me! It's my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hurt... because you think I'm in love with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not true. There is nothing between him and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the only one who matters to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really. Please believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies! Those are all lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In the snow when you said "let's die", it wasn't for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because he hurt you so badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...you had to drag me into your pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That wasn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only for you and me! No one else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have eyes only for you. You alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to see you the way you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stay away from you so I don't see how you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Or... shall we go both at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That would be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll fly like birds, and in that brief moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll trust you a hundred times... a thousand times... more than now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. I saw your proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No more! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some chicken stew, with lots of vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked all over for you. But I knew you'd come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would. I was sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd want something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone you loved asked you to die with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...could you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never thought about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely never!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... No! No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's mustn't happen! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.41,0:22:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.85,0:22:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A week passed, then something else happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san, Shinobu-san is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.46,0:22:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Mariko-san! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I came over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to stay overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I stay over, in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,0:22:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good... don't worry, just one night, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.52,0:22:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't ask me why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... what about your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:22:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked them already. Sorry for the intrusion. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:23:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, great! Your bed is softer than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Light out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I didn't call.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.93,0:23:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.05,0:23:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.91,0:23:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.31,0:23:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother... It's about Mariko-san. She is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:14.16,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:19.63,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:25.24,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.24,0:24:30.71,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.45,0:24:36.99,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.99,0:24:42.46,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.46,0:24:45.19,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.19,0:24:48.00,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.00,0:24:50.40,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.40,0:24:55.67,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
